Home > Entertainment > Soulja Boy Tells 50 Cent To "Shut The F*ck Up" Over Robbery Accusations Soulja Boy Tells 50 Cent To "Shut The F*ck Up" Over Robbery Accusations 8 28 Posted by Trevor Smith , Jan 7, 2017 at 02:27pm Soulja's beef tour continues. 
Soulja Boy is not happy with 50 Cent 's suggestion that he was robbed in L.A. yesterday. After 50 took to Instagram to claim that Soulja had his chain taken, and make further arrangements for the rapper's proposed boxing match with Chris Brown (it's a long story ), Soulja fired back on the same platform. 
Soulja posted a picture of himself holding two firearms and tucking another in his pocket on IG today, reserving the caption for 50 Cent. "Rob who take what somebody tell Curtis Jackson shut the fuck up," he wrote. A photo posted by Soulja Boy (@souljaboy) on Jan 7, 2017 at 7:51am PST 
While 50 is the latest rapper Soulja has sparred with online, his beef with Chris Brown is still ongoing, so he reserved some posts for the singer as well. SB posted a photo of himself and a woman with the caption "Aye Chris I Fucked yo bitch," which he followed up with a side by side of himself and Chris with the same woman. A photo posted by Soulja Boy (@souljaboy) on Jan 7, 2017 at 7:58am PST A photo posted by Soulja Boy (@souljaboy) on Jan 7, 2017 at 8:08am PST A photo posted by Soulja Boy (@souljaboy) on Jan 7, 2017 at 8:22am PST
